definition.value: A glycosyl alditol derivative that is N-acetyl-D-galactosaminitol in which the hydroxy group at position 3 has been glycosylated by an alpha-D-galactopyranosyl group.
A monosaccharide sulfate that is beta-D-glucopyranose in which the hydroxy group at position 3 has been converted into the corresponding hydrogen sulfate derivative.
